Hope you enjoy all of them…

It’s been another record-breaking month for @myworldpod ! 

#AEW #AEWDynamite #AEWRampage #WWE #WWERAW #WWESMACKDOWN

Rest in Peace and Power Don West:

When I received the text from Don’s wife, Terri, earlier today on his passing I had an overwhelming feeling of mixed emotions—so happy and relieved for him that he was out of pain and his cancer was gone; but, the finality of his death was so dark and it hurt. 

We FaceTimed just a few days ago — and because of his situation it’s the only conversation that I’ve ever had with him that I got to do all the talking — and I’m sure he hated that!ha. We reminisced, laughed, and I got the final opportunity to tell him I loved him and that I will see him again one day! 

This picture is from the last time we were on stage together — Chicago Starrcast. 

I will miss my buddy…

Love ❤️ ya D-Dub!

The last 5 episodes(#86-90) of @myworldpod Cover Art! 

From Paul Walterhausen, the NWO, the 4 Horsemen, SlapMax Caster, Vince Russo, the Queen’s laser shot, and much, much more…we covered a lot of ground over these journeys!

And, one of my favorite, most emotional and enjoyable episodes paying tribute to my friend, Don West!

Enjoy!
